    "en": {
      "title": "7,000 MT of fuel to be delivered today (25)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CPC) announced that 7,000 MT of Fuel will be distributed throughout the country today (25).",
        "The Ceylon Petroleum Corporation further said 4,000 MT of diesel and 3,000 MT of petrol will be distributed to CEYPETCO filling stations.",
        "However, there is no final decision on the implementation of the QR bases system for the distribution of fuel in the country.",
        "The Chairman of the All Ceylon Petrol Station Owners\u2019 Association Kumara Rajapaksa said that fuel will be issued from filling stations according to the last digit of the vehicle\u2019s registration number, today as well until the green light is given to implement the QR bases system for the distribution of fuel.",
        "F1: Verstappen wins French Grand Prix after Leclerc crashes out"
      ],
